# Branch 3.x (stable)

This is the main branch of **awesome** and gets all new features and bug fixes.

Latest stable version of **awesome** is version 3.1 (codename: *Helicopter*) released on 12th December 2008.

* [v3.1 changelog](/changelogs/v3.1) ([short](/changelogs/short/v3.1))
* [awesome-3.1.tar.gz](awesome-3.1.tar.gz)
* [awesome-3.1.tar.bz2](awesome-3.1.tar.bz2)

# Branch 2.x (old stable)

This branch of **awesome** is deprecated. However bug fixes are still welcome.

Latest old stable version of **awesome** is version 2.3.5 (codename: *New Morning*) released on 2nd January 2009.

* [v2.3.5 changelog](/changelogs/v2.3.5) ([short](/changelogs/short/v2.3.5))
* [awesome-2.3.5.tar.gz](awesome-2.3.5.tar.gz)
* [awesome-2.3.5.tar.bz2](awesome-2.3.5.tar.bz2)

# Development

Development versions of **awesome** can be downloaded as tarballs using git snapshot [here](http://git.naquadah.org/?p=awesome.git;a=summary).

You can also grab a git copy by running:

  `git clone git://git.naquadah.org/awesome.git`

